window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A single mom.</b></p> <p><b>His first love.</b></p> <p><b>A reunion they never expected.</b></p> <p>Andi Harmon wanted nothing more to marry Prince Charming. Her best friend Kyle Davenport believed he’d be that man.&nbsp;But after losing the girl of his dreams to the town bad boy, Kyle left Rosewood Bay and swore he’d never look back.</p> <p>But Kyle returns to his hometown to discover Andi is still there...and available if he can break down the walls around her heart.</p> <p><b>This book was formerly called </b><b><i>Dream</i></b><b>. No changes from original. </b></p>"; 
